  "transliteration": "śhrī-bhagavān uvācha\nparaṁ bhūyaḥ pravakṣhyāmi jñānānāṁ jñānam uttamam\nyaj jñātvā munayaḥ sarve parāṁ siddhim ito gatāḥ",
